{"tid":619395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港都中］大陸沙塵到台灣北海岸　台氣象局副局長：外出應戴口罩","createTime":"2018-04-06T15:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T15:06:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c082f32ee45a038b9c679da7868b6aeb9a58d1ea","tid":619395,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/230346_db26f02c03d36e57d47a34087b55f6b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F230346_db26f02c03d36e57d47a34087b55f6b2.png&h=f664ee38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中央氣象局副局長鄭明典稍早在臉書表示，大陸的沙塵到北海岸了，建議民眾關閉面風向的門窗，陽台上的衣服拿進室內，外出戴口罩會有幫助。 鄭明典解釋，鋒面後的北風將大陸霾和沙塵往南推了，雖一度被鋒面雨帶擋住，但風場條件仍然持續將PM2.5往南推，現大陸的沙塵到北海岸了，民眾應多加留意。（生活中心／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180406/1329687/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180406%2F1329687%2F&d=v%2FFFyb0r89fiJAo8Co9bFr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=ba494fbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180406%2F1329687%2F&h=b9a24282\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180406/1329687/</a>"},{"pid":"5dd95ff4c692a7a5845df63aeaaa5557d34aa91a","tid":619395,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}